<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90cbcc0f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s6961"><num value="6961">§ 6961.</num><heading> Establishment of Task Force</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is hereby established a task force on prohibition of importation of products of forced or prison labor from the People’s Republic of China (hereafter in this part referred to as the “Task Force”).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90cbcc10-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/286/dB/tV/s501">Pub. L. 106–286, div. B, title V, § 501</ref>, <date date="2000-10-10">Oct. 10, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/903">114 Stat. 903</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
